 <h1>{{ page.title }}</h1>
	<p> 
		Here, you will find a summary of the popularization projects I made. Most projects are in French, they will probably be translated at some point in the future. This future becomes nearer
		if I know someone is interested in one of the project, so feel free to ask me!
	</p>
	
	<h3><a href="/popularization/hyperbolique/">Géométrie hyperbolique</a></h3>
	<p>
		This pages contains the sources and material for a talk I gave for the Clubmath of Université de Montréal on 23-09-2020.
		
		Dans cette page se trouvent les références et le matériel pour mon exposé au Clubmath de l'Université de Montréal du 23-09-2020.	
	</p>
	
